data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News Jupiter announced that it has launched a Meme art bounty experiment with Drip Haus with "culture" as the core, inviting community users to send any Meme tokens to the designated address CCFRRLa5qvykEuxN5XjwBGGj9QNrBmpa4NegyfbVk5Tk as the bounty pool for the corresponding artworks of the project. Jupiter said that it will select tokens with stories or high bounties, and display related community artworks on its platform token page and gallery to reflect the cultural diversity behind Meme coins.
The time nodes of this activity are as follows:
Before April 21: Token submission deadline;
Before April 30: Creators submit artworks;
Before May 5: Officials of each community must announce the selected works on the X platform. If not announced, the organizer will decide on their behalf.
Jupiter emphasized that this activity is an open experiment, and users are requested to participate at their discretion and avoid investing assets that they cannot afford.
